      "content": "Yeah, it is more restrictive. The main change is that the Lite kernel won't have access to your high-level predictive modeling or the complex trajectory planning modules. It'll mostly just stick to basic lane keeping and obstacle braking. It's much simpler and less likely to make \"unpredictable\" decisions, which is what the board wants.",
